<noinclude>This template is a sidebar for displaying key statistics about a person.

==Usage==

<pre>
{{Userbox
| name                   =
| gravatar               =
| affiliation            =
| github                 =
| stackoverflow          =
| openhub                =
| osrc                   =
| website                =
}}
</pre>

==Example==
{{Userbox
| name                   = John Smith
| gravatar               = 7194e8d48fa1d2b689f99443b767316c
| affiliation            = The Institute of Awesome
| github                 = octocat
| stackoverflow          = 22656/jon-skeet
